When I first listened to the chorus in some of the reels & shorts, I thought it is a nursery rhyme because the chorus sung by the females is so cute (The Khalasi thingy), I couldn't think of any other than children. However, when I saw a short about this song on Brut India, it compelled me to listen to this entire song. After listening to the song for the first time, there is no turning back.❤✌️

For me it is SONG OF THE YEAR & a song we can come back to everytime.
